### [NEW] [core/detector.py](file:///d:/DRDO%20PROJECT%20-%20Copy/core/detector.py)

Advanced detection engine:
- **Multi-model fusion**: Runs pose + face + person detection with optimized inference
- **Confidence filtering**: Only accepts detections above configurable thresholds
- **Keypoint validation**: Checks if shoulder/hip keypoints have sufficient confidence before using them
- **NMS (Non-Maximum Suppression)**: Prevents duplicate detections across models
- **GPU acceleration**: Auto-detects CUDA and uses it when available

---

### [NEW] [core/heart_estimator.py](file:///d:/DRDO%20PROJECT%20-%20Copy/core/heart_estimator.py)

**Anatomical heart position estimation** (replaces hardcoded offsets):
- Uses **torso proportional calculation**: The heart is ~30% down the torso (between shoulders and hips), slightly left of center
- Falls back to shoulder-only estimation when hips aren't visible
- Uses **body bounding box scaling** so it works at any distance/zoom level
- Returns confidence score for the heart position estimate
- Draws anatomical reference lines and zones

---

### [NEW] [core/tracker.py](file:///d:/DRDO%20PROJECT%20-%20Copy/core/tracker.py)

Multi-target tracking system:
- **IOU-based tracker**: Associates detections across frames using Intersection over Union
- **Unique target IDs**: Each person gets a persistent ID (T-001, T-002, etc.)
- **Track history**: Stores last N positions for trajectory prediction
- **Track state management**: NEW → TRACKING → LOST → DELETED lifecycle
- **Velocity estimation**: Predicts next-frame position for smoother tracking

---

### [NEW] [core/firing_system.py](file:///d:/DRDO%20PROJECT%20-%20Copy/core/firing_system.py)

Simulated auto-firing system:
- **Target lock-on**: Requires target to be stable for N frames before engaging
- **Engagement zones**: GREEN (safe) → YELLOW (warning) → RED (fire-ready)
- **Firing simulation**: Visual laser line + muzzle flash animation on screen
- **Hit confirmation**: Draws impact marker on heart position
- **Cooldown system**: Prevents rapid re-engagement
- **Sound alerts**: Optional beep sounds for lock-on and firing events
- **Keyboard controls**: Toggle auto-fire, manual fire, safety lock

